{{ Infobox V8 Supercar race report | flag = Queensland | title = 2014 Castrol Townsville 500 | round_no = 7 | season_no = 14 | year = 2014 | series = IVSC | track_map = Townsville (Australia) street circuit track map.svg | date = 4–6 July | location = [[Townsville, Queensland|Townsville]], [[Queensland]] | circuit = Townsville Street Circuit | weather = Fine | race1_laps = 44 | race1_dist = 125 | pole1 = [[James Courtney]] | pole1_team = [[Holden Racing Team]] | pole1_time = 1:12.8026 | winner1 = [[Jamie Whincup]] | winner1_team = [[Triple Eight Race Engineering (Australia)|Triple Eight Race Engineering]] | winner1_time = 59:48.1702 | race2_laps = 44 | race2_dist = 125 | pole2 = [[Fabian Coulthard]] | pole2_team = [[Brad Jones Racing]] | pole2_time = 1:13.0169 | winner2 = [[Garth Tander]] | winner2_team = [[Holden Racing Team]] | winner2_time = 57:38.3580 | race3_laps = 88 | race3_dist = 250 | pole3 = [[Craig Lowndes]] | pole3_team = [[Triple Eight Race Engineering (Australia)|Triple Eight Race Engineering]] | pole3_time = 1:13.0978 | winner3 = [[Jamie Whincup]] | winner3_team = [[Triple Eight Race Engineering (Australia)|Triple Eight Race Engineering]] | winner3_time = 1:54:24.2583 }}
The '''2014 Castrol Townsville 500 - Driven by TAFE Queensland''' was a motor race meeting for the Australian sedan-based [[V8 Supercars]]. It was the seventh event of the [[2014 International V8 Supercars Championship]]. It was held on the weekend of 4-6 July at the [[Townsville Street Circuit]], at [[Townsville, Queensland|Townsville]], [[Queensland, Australia|Queensland]].
