{{coord|58|20|50|N|11|56|35|E|source:svwiki_region:SE_type:landmark|display=title}}
'''Agnebergshallen''' is an indoor arena for sports events and concerts in [[Uddevalla]], [[Sweden]]. The arena, which was inaugurated in 1987, has a capacity for 2.400 during sports events.<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.uddevalla.se/uppleva-och-gora/idrott-motion-och-friluftsliv/hallar-och-idrottsanlaggningar/agnebergshallen.html|title=Agnebergshallen - Uddevalla kommun|website=www.uddevalla.se|language=sv|access-date=2016-12-02}}</ref> It is the home arena of both the man and woman section of the handball club [[Kroppskultur]] (Kroppskultur Herr, Kroppskultur Dam). Both in the Swedish elite.<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.svenskhandboll.se/Fleraresultatsidor/AKTUELLAMATCHER/?VenueId=2362&s=2014|title=Agnebergshallen - AKTUELLA MATCHER - Svenska Handbollförbundet - IdrottOnline Forbund|website=www.svenskhandboll.se|access-date=2016-12-02}}</ref>

