'''Clube Atlético Monte Líbano''', or C.A. Monte Líbano, is a [[Brazil]]ian men's professional [[basketball]] club that is based in [[Brazil]].

==History==
Monte Líbano won the [[Campeonato Brasileiro de Basquete|Brazilian League]] championship 5 times, in the years 1982, 1984, 1985, 1986, and 1987. They also won the [[South American Club Championship]] twice, in the years 1985 and 1986.

