{{Infobox football club | clubname = Nashe Pivo | image = Nashe_Pivo_FC_Logo.png | fullname = FC Nashe Pivo | nickname = | founded = {{Start date and age|2003}} | ground = [[Stadium Abdish-Ata]], [[Kant, Kyrgyzstan|Kant]], [[Kyrgyzstan]] | capacity = 2,000 | chairman = | manager = | league = | season = | position = }}
'''FC Nashe Pivo''' is a [[Kyrgyzstan]]i football club based in [[Kant, Kyrgyzstan|Kant]], Kyrgyzstan that played in the second division in Kyrgyzstan. It's a farm club of [[FC Abdish-Ata Kant]].
== History == *2003: Founded as ''FC Abdish-Ata-2 Kant''. *20.05.2003: Renamed to ''FC Nashe Pivo Kant''.
Nashe Pivo reached the [[Kyrgyzstan Cup]] Final for the first time in 2015, where they were defeated 4-2 by parent club [[FC Abdysh-Ata Kant|Abdysh-Ata Kant]].<ref>{{cite web|title="Абдыш-Ата" – 4-х кратный Обладатель Кубка Кыргызстана|url=http://www.flk.kg/ru/node/1274|website=flk.kg/|publisher=Football League Kyrgyzstan|accessdate=27 October 2015|language=Russian|date=24 October 2015}}{{dead link|date=September 2017 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>
== Achievements == '''[[Kyrgyzstan League]]:'''
'''[[Kyrgyzstan Cup]]:''' *Finalist: 2015 *Quarterfinalist: 2013, 2014
