{{Infobox handball club | clubname = IUVENTA Michalovce | image = Iuventa Michalovce 2010 11.jpg | fullname = HK IUVENTA Michalovce | short name = | founded = 1976 | ground = Chemkostav Arena, Michalovce | capacity = 1,800 | chairman = Gabriel Dorič<ref name=staff>{{cite web|url=http://www.iuventa-zhk.chemkostavarena.sk/?stranka=o_klube|title=O klube|trans-title=About the club|publisher=HK IUVENTA Michalovce official website|accessdate=29 November 2011|language=Slovak}}</ref> | manager = František Urban | league = WHIL | season = 2016–17 | position = WHIL Slovak Final, 1st | website = http://www.iuventa-zhk.chemkostavarena.sk | colour1 = yellow | colour2 = blue | colour3 = | pattern_la1 = | pattern_b1 = | pattern_ra1 = | pattern_sh1 = | leftarm1 = | body1 = | rightarm1 = | shorts1 = | pattern_la2 = | pattern_b2 = | pattern_ra2 = | pattern_sh2 = | leftarm2 = | body2 = | rightarm2 = | shorts2 = }}
'''IUVENTA Michalovce''' is a Slovak [[team handball|handball]] club based in [[Michalovce]], that plays in the Women's Handball International League (WHIL), an international championship organized for Czech and Slovak teams.
