{{one source|date=April 2014}} {{Infobox football club | clubname = SC de Bangui| image = | fullname = Sporting Club de Bangui| nickname = | founded = | ground = [[Barthelemy Boganda Stadium]]| capacity = 35000| chairman = Jean-Marie Lorenzon| manager = | league = [[Central African Republic League]]| season = 2013| position = 2nd| }}
'''Sporting Club de Bangui''' is a [[football (soccer)]] club from the [[Central African Republic]] based in [[Bangui]].<ref>http://www.thefinalball.com/equipa.php?id=28357</ref>
The team plays in the [[Central African Republic League]].
==Stadium== Currently the team plays at the 35000 capacity [[Barthelemy Boganda Stadium]].
==Performance in CAF competitions== *[[1979 African Cup Winners' Cup]] *[[1981 African Cup of Champions Clubs]] *[[1993 African Cup of Champions Clubs]] *[[1998 African Cup Winners' Cup]]
